        "title": "[api-minor] Always allow e.g. rendering to continue even if there are errors, and add a `stopAtErrors` parameter to `getDocument` to opt-out of this behaviour (issue 6342, issue 3795, bug 1130815)",
        "user": {
            "login": "Snuffleupagus",
            "id": 2692120,
            "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI2OTIxMjA=",
